1
00:00:22,464 --> 00:00:26,432
♪Should we forget yesterday's sorrows♪

2
00:00:26,432 --> 00:00:29,728
♪And the dazed confusion♪

3
00:00:30,976 --> 00:00:33,681
♪Should we let go of♪

4
00:00:33,681 --> 00:00:35,904
♪The stubborn madness♪

5
00:00:35,904 --> 00:00:39,072
♪And naive recklessness now♪

6
00:00:40,192 --> 00:00:43,840
♪Those years, those faces♪

7
00:00:44,992 --> 00:00:48,763
♪Those old scars we can't erase♪

8
00:00:49,824 --> 00:00:52,460
♪Tears streaming, facing the light♪

9
00:00:53,152 --> 00:00:57,594
♪Piercing the sorrow within♪

10
00:01:08,716 --> 00:01:12,736
♪The road ahead's long,
stumbling all the way♪

11
00:01:13,536 --> 00:01:18,076
♪The wounds we've borne
are medals hidden within♪

12
00:01:18,336 --> 00:01:22,391
♪Standing alone on an open plain♪

13
00:01:23,168 --> 00:01:26,851
♪We gaze at the stars♪

14
00:01:31,228 --> 00:01:34,816
=The Dream Maker=

15
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,927
=Episode 26=

16
00:01:38,674 --> 00:01:40,394
Hello, Mr. Xia.

17
00:01:42,593 --> 00:01:43,153
Well,

18
00:01:44,114 --> 00:01:46,593
Yuehai's accounts were
temporarily frozen by investigators.

19
00:01:46,834 --> 00:01:49,048
They can't be unfrozen
until the investigation ends.

20
00:01:49,528 --> 00:01:52,634
But Yuehai currently
has many ongoing projects.

21
00:01:53,034 --> 00:01:54,653
- They can't stop.
- Right.

22
00:01:54,713 --> 00:01:57,593
I was wondering if the county
could advance Yuehai

23
00:01:58,433 --> 00:01:59,313
some funds.

24
00:01:59,994 --> 00:02:00,914
Designated funds.

25
00:02:02,593 --> 00:02:03,093
Right.

26
00:02:05,994 --> 00:02:06,953
Okay, okay.

27
00:02:07,233 --> 00:02:09,994
I'll draft a report immediately
and send it to the county.

28
00:02:11,153 --> 00:02:11,994
Thank you, Mr. Xia.

29
00:02:13,433 --> 00:02:14,313
Goodbye, Mr. Xia.

30
00:02:22,873 --> 00:02:24,153
Any other questions?

31
00:02:26,753 --> 00:02:28,674
(Chats under 5 minutes)
Ms. Li, I'm heading to the site now.

32
00:02:28,994 --> 00:02:29,794
I'll get them back

33
00:02:30,514 --> 00:02:31,913
to resume work.

34
00:02:32,274 --> 00:02:34,394
Good, and explain that to them.

35
00:02:34,633 --> 00:02:36,674
Site payments will be settled
in three days.

36
00:02:37,153 --> 00:02:39,433
But you also need to warn the foremen.

37
00:02:39,794 --> 00:02:42,433
While Mr. Zheng is away,
anyone who dares to play tricks

38
00:02:43,033 --> 00:02:43,873
or scheme deviously,

39
00:02:44,473 --> 00:02:47,554
or messes with the project quality
will bear the consequences.

40
00:02:48,074 --> 00:02:48,574
Understood.

41
00:02:48,913 --> 00:02:49,834
Ms. Li, don't worry.

42
00:02:49,954 --> 00:02:51,074
I'm keeping an eye on it.

43
00:02:51,954 --> 00:02:52,454
Okay.

44
00:02:55,213 --> 00:02:57,114
Ms. Li, our finances
are so tight right now.

45
00:02:57,234 --> 00:02:58,193
I have a proposal.

46
00:02:58,834 --> 00:03:01,114
All cadres, including us,

47
00:03:01,193 --> 00:03:03,834
could temporarily suspend our salaries
starting this month.

48
00:03:04,153 --> 00:03:05,794
That could save us some funds

49
00:03:05,913 --> 00:03:07,753
to use where it's most needed, right?

50
00:03:10,114 --> 00:03:10,614
Alright.

51
00:03:11,954 --> 00:03:13,954
But you must
thoroughly explain it to them.

52
00:03:14,473 --> 00:03:15,394
Don't force anyone.

53
00:03:16,274 --> 00:03:17,674
I think everyone will understand.

54
00:03:17,794 --> 00:03:18,593
I'll go do that now.

55
00:03:20,913 --> 00:03:21,593
Mr. Xie.

56
00:03:22,074 --> 00:03:24,074
I'm off to the Power Supply Bureau
for Wang Defa.

57
00:03:24,433 --> 00:03:26,913
If he dares cut Yuehai's power,
I'll camp out there.

58
00:03:28,153 --> 00:03:28,653
Wait.

59
00:03:34,074 --> 00:03:35,994
A friend gave me an herbal prescription.

60
00:03:37,033 --> 00:03:39,354
It's good for kidney health.

61
00:03:39,674 --> 00:03:41,994
Wang Defa's kidneys aren't great.
Take this to him.

62
00:03:43,954 --> 00:03:46,574
He supplies power to Yuehai,
and you supply vitality to him, huh?

63
00:03:47,354 --> 00:03:48,033
Carrot and stick.

64
00:03:48,274 --> 00:03:48,774
Got it.

65
00:03:48,834 --> 00:03:49,433
Xie.

66
00:03:50,554 --> 00:03:53,193
You should also check on Xuemei.

67
00:03:55,674 --> 00:03:56,174
I know.

68
00:03:57,954 --> 00:03:58,713
You look exhausted.

69
00:03:59,794 --> 00:04:01,873
Don't stress about Mr. Zheng or us.

70
00:04:02,274 --> 00:04:03,074
Get more rest.

71
00:04:22,674 --> 00:04:23,513
With too fast a drip,

72
00:04:23,794 --> 00:04:25,753
it speeds up blood flow
throughout the body,

73
00:04:26,234 --> 00:04:27,873
putting immense pressure on the heart.

74
00:04:28,114 --> 00:04:30,953
It could also damage liver
and kidney function

75
00:04:31,154 --> 00:04:32,273
and cause GI irritation.

76
00:04:38,714 --> 00:04:39,833
You can take off your mask.

77
00:04:40,114 --> 00:04:41,674
No other patients will come in here.

78
00:04:42,073 --> 00:04:44,474
You can lie down
and get the IV properly.

79
00:04:44,753 --> 00:04:45,914
No one will disturb you.

80
00:04:46,953 --> 00:04:48,114
Thank you, Director Jiang.

81
00:04:51,313 --> 00:04:53,034
Upper respiratory infection.

82
00:04:53,354 --> 00:04:56,273
Your white blood cell
and neutrophil counts are both too high.

83
00:04:58,313 --> 00:04:59,674
The medicine is prescribed.

84
00:05:00,034 --> 00:05:01,313
Be sure to take it properly.

85
00:05:01,914 --> 00:05:03,554
Bring those counts down.

86
00:05:06,354 --> 00:05:06,854
Come in.

87
00:05:07,193 --> 00:05:08,953
Director Jiang,
the granules you asked for.

88
00:05:09,273 --> 00:05:09,773
Thank you.

89
00:05:13,633 --> 00:05:14,154
Ma'am,

90
00:05:16,674 --> 00:05:17,873
Du Tao and I broke up.

91
00:05:23,313 --> 00:05:25,393
I don't want to hide it from you.

92
00:05:29,034 --> 00:05:30,513
And you've probably heard,

93
00:05:31,034 --> 00:05:32,594
Mr. Zheng is under investigation.

94
00:05:33,554 --> 00:05:36,794
There have indeed been
some rumors lately.

95
00:05:44,193 --> 00:05:46,513
For someone with tonsillitis,

96
00:05:47,114 --> 00:05:49,554
drink more water and talk less.

97
00:05:50,313 --> 00:05:51,474
I'm telling you this

98
00:05:51,914 --> 00:05:53,714
mainly because I hope these two matters

99
00:05:54,234 --> 00:05:56,554
won't affect your decision
to stay in Yuehai.

100
00:05:59,273 --> 00:06:00,193
Then tell me,

101
00:06:01,234 --> 00:06:03,873
what reason
could you give for me to stay?

102
00:06:09,273 --> 00:06:10,114
Actually, I know

103
00:06:10,594 --> 00:06:13,273
that from the start, you chose to stay
as Director here in Yuehai

104
00:06:13,273 --> 00:06:15,193
not because of my relationship
with Du Tao.

105
00:06:16,073 --> 00:06:17,393
Moreover, you promised me

106
00:06:17,554 --> 00:06:18,833
that over two years,

107
00:06:18,994 --> 00:06:21,144
you'd train an independent,
excellent surgical team.

108
00:06:21,914 --> 00:06:24,953
And also because I submitted a report
to the province

109
00:06:25,193 --> 00:06:26,513
to apply for

110
00:06:26,594 --> 00:06:28,554
neonatal surgery R&D funding for Yuehai

111
00:06:29,114 --> 00:06:30,753
and reserve
the latest medical equipment.

112
00:06:31,474 --> 00:06:33,873
These are our promises
and agreements to each other.

113
00:06:34,313 --> 00:06:35,594
They haven't been fulfilled yet.

114
00:06:36,354 --> 00:06:37,433
So, Director Jiang,

115
00:06:38,554 --> 00:06:39,433
you can't leave yet.

116
00:06:43,513 --> 00:06:44,234
Are you done?

117
00:06:44,513 --> 00:06:45,013
Not yet.

118
00:06:45,633 --> 00:06:46,313
What else?

119
00:06:47,914 --> 00:06:48,753
Also because...

120
00:06:49,833 --> 00:06:50,914
you can't resist good food.

121
00:06:51,833 --> 00:06:53,554
Yuehai has the best seafood.

122
00:06:55,273 --> 00:06:56,873
Who says only the seafood is good?

123
00:06:57,914 --> 00:07:00,354
Yuehai's stir-fried noodles
are my favorite.

124
00:07:01,513 --> 00:07:03,714
Chief Sun of ER requests you,
Director Jiang.

125
00:07:04,354 --> 00:07:04,914
Got it.

126
00:07:07,393 --> 00:07:09,914
Don't worry, I'm not leaving.

127
00:07:12,154 --> 00:07:14,633
After all, my son wrote that article.

128
00:07:15,513 --> 00:07:17,594
And those grand plans
you just mentioned.

129
00:07:18,234 --> 00:07:20,873
I want to see you fulfill your promises.

130
00:07:22,273 --> 00:07:22,914
I will.

131
00:07:25,354 --> 00:07:27,633
Just call the head nurse
when you finish the IV.

132
00:07:27,794 --> 00:07:29,994
The inflammation levels
in your body are too high.

133
00:07:30,354 --> 00:07:32,253
You must rest properly, understand?

134
00:07:32,873 --> 00:07:33,474
I will.

135
00:07:35,313 --> 00:07:37,273
Will you?

136
00:07:42,433 --> 00:07:43,154
Ms. Li,

137
00:07:45,753 --> 00:07:47,833
as a woman, I truly admire you.

138
00:07:49,354 --> 00:07:51,154
But as Du Tao's mother,

139
00:07:51,914 --> 00:07:53,313
I feel pity for you both.

140
00:07:54,433 --> 00:07:57,393
On my son's behalf, I just want to say

141
00:07:57,994 --> 00:07:58,674
I'm sorry.

142
00:07:59,994 --> 00:08:01,674
Actually, I've also noticed

143
00:08:02,234 --> 00:08:03,674
Du Tao's recent changes.

144
00:08:04,193 --> 00:08:05,554
Now I feel more and more

145
00:08:06,234 --> 00:08:08,674
that you two might not be a good match.

146
00:08:10,114 --> 00:08:12,914
When you just told me you've broken up,

147
00:08:14,433 --> 00:08:17,753
I was relieved for you
from the bottom of my heart.

148
00:08:36,553 --> 00:08:37,673
Ping, you're here.

149
00:08:38,194 --> 00:08:39,393
Granny, I came to see you.

150
00:08:40,994 --> 00:08:42,954
You brought me so much food again.

151
00:08:43,153 --> 00:08:44,913
I can't finish it all by myself.

152
00:08:45,314 --> 00:08:47,033
It's okay.
Just take your time eating it.

153
00:08:47,834 --> 00:08:49,153
This month's living expenses.

154
00:08:49,393 --> 00:08:50,673
I'll put it away for you here.

155
00:08:50,873 --> 00:08:51,753
No need.

156
00:08:51,913 --> 00:08:53,873
I didn't even finish last month's.

157
00:08:54,194 --> 00:08:56,153
Xiaohai called me.

158
00:08:56,753 --> 00:08:58,434
He's doing well in there.

159
00:08:59,194 --> 00:09:00,474
He'll be out soon.

160
00:09:00,873 --> 00:09:02,074
So, don't worry anymore.

161
00:09:03,994 --> 00:09:06,194
You always think about me,

162
00:09:06,553 --> 00:09:09,594
giving this old lady something
to look forward to from time to time...

163
00:09:11,234 --> 00:09:12,033
Have some water.

164
00:09:12,474 --> 00:09:13,194
I'll help myself.

165
00:09:56,594 --> 00:09:58,393
There's no show on this TV.

166
00:09:58,834 --> 00:09:59,793
What are you watching?

167
00:10:02,474 --> 00:10:03,633
In this room,

168
00:10:04,114 --> 00:10:07,194
it's nice to have some noise.

169
00:10:10,714 --> 00:10:11,214
Yes.

170
00:10:18,513 --> 00:10:19,153
Ping,

171
00:10:20,673 --> 00:10:23,074
did something happen?

172
00:10:29,673 --> 00:10:30,673
I ran into some trouble.

173
00:10:34,873 --> 00:10:36,994
Don't worry. It'll all pass.

174
00:10:38,033 --> 00:10:38,533
Look.

175
00:10:38,753 --> 00:10:42,834
I've been through the old society.
I have seen everything.

176
00:10:43,553 --> 00:10:45,633
But I'm still living well now.

177
00:11:00,434 --> 00:11:01,633
Granny, I have to go now.

178
00:11:05,714 --> 00:11:06,553
Take care.

179
00:11:25,434 --> 00:11:26,033
Xuemei.

180
00:11:26,314 --> 00:11:26,834
I'm back.

181
00:11:27,793 --> 00:11:28,913
Where on earth did you go?

182
00:11:29,913 --> 00:11:30,994
I didn't sleep all night.

183
00:11:31,314 --> 00:11:33,273
I was swamped
with customer cancellations all day.

184
00:11:33,816 --> 00:11:35,913
Also, all self-employed individuals
on Binhai Road

185
00:11:35,913 --> 00:11:37,513
were questioned by the Municipal DIC.

186
00:11:37,913 --> 00:11:39,194
But they couldn't find you.

187
00:11:39,934 --> 00:11:41,033
Well, say something.

188
00:11:41,153 --> 00:11:42,553
Where did you go? I was frantic.

189
00:11:42,553 --> 00:11:43,594
I know, I know.

190
00:11:44,153 --> 00:11:44,653
By the way,

191
00:11:45,074 --> 00:11:47,673
go tell everyone to come here
for a meeting in two hours.

192
00:11:48,153 --> 00:11:50,033
What do you mean?
Did you find a solution?

193
00:11:50,553 --> 00:11:52,114
We'll talk when they get here. Just go.

194
00:11:52,793 --> 00:11:53,434
In two hours?

195
00:11:53,873 --> 00:11:54,393
Okay.

196
00:11:56,954 --> 00:11:57,553
My neck...

197
00:12:06,793 --> 00:12:07,354
Morning, sir.

198
00:12:09,633 --> 00:12:11,513
Xuemei, let me introduce him.

199
00:12:11,773 --> 00:12:12,273
This is...

200
00:12:12,273 --> 00:12:14,354
No need. I'll introduce myself.

201
00:12:14,994 --> 00:12:15,494
Ms. Gao,

202
00:12:16,074 --> 00:12:18,954
I'm Liu Weimin, head of
the Municipal DIC investigation team.

203
00:12:19,393 --> 00:12:22,234
We have a few questions for you.
It will take about half an hour.

204
00:12:23,793 --> 00:12:24,293
Okay.

205
00:12:29,354 --> 00:12:30,033
May we begin?

206
00:12:30,434 --> 00:12:31,314
Yes.

207
00:12:35,074 --> 00:12:35,594
Well...

208
00:12:36,954 --> 00:12:39,114
Sorry, there's not much to offer you.

209
00:12:39,393 --> 00:12:40,314
No need.

210
00:12:40,474 --> 00:12:41,194
Sunflower seeds?

211
00:12:41,194 --> 00:12:42,033
No need.

212
00:12:42,393 --> 00:12:42,994
You go ahead.

213
00:12:43,694 --> 00:12:44,194
No.

214
00:12:44,194 --> 00:12:44,694
You can eat.

215
00:12:45,273 --> 00:12:45,793
I can?

216
00:12:46,753 --> 00:12:47,253
Yes.

217
00:12:47,753 --> 00:12:50,033
I've been busy outside since yesterday.

218
00:12:50,913 --> 00:12:52,513
I missed my meals. I am indeed hungry.

219
00:12:52,753 --> 00:12:53,314
I understand.

220
00:12:53,474 --> 00:12:54,074
Sorry.

221
00:12:54,194 --> 00:12:54,694
It's fine.

222
00:12:54,793 --> 00:12:55,544
You're not eating?

223
00:12:57,633 --> 00:12:58,673
Mr. Zheng

224
00:12:59,273 --> 00:13:01,873
owns multiple properties in town.
Do you know that?

225
00:13:03,114 --> 00:13:03,913
I don't know.

226
00:13:04,553 --> 00:13:06,793
I truly... Sorry. I truly don't know.

227
00:13:07,513 --> 00:13:08,954
I think that's probably a rumor.

228
00:13:09,434 --> 00:13:11,913
Just tell us whether you know or not.

229
00:13:12,234 --> 00:13:14,633
As for whether it's a rumor or not,
we will investigate.

230
00:13:14,753 --> 00:13:15,393
Okay.

231
00:13:17,474 --> 00:13:21,114
We've heard that this place
is called 'Little Wall Street.'

232
00:13:21,673 --> 00:13:24,234
All the town's business money
flows through you.

233
00:13:24,793 --> 00:13:25,293
Right?

234
00:13:25,673 --> 00:13:27,194
That's a bit exaggerated, sir.

235
00:13:27,513 --> 00:13:29,834
My factory was the first place
in town to get a telephone.

236
00:13:30,074 --> 00:13:32,354
So folks came here
to make calls and do business.

237
00:13:32,913 --> 00:13:34,994
Now people have their own phones.

238
00:13:35,194 --> 00:13:36,153
So they come less often.

239
00:13:37,153 --> 00:13:38,033
Also,

240
00:13:38,673 --> 00:13:40,714
it's true many 'monkeys' trust me.

241
00:13:40,793 --> 00:13:43,114
Their money goes through me.
But not all of them.

242
00:13:45,954 --> 00:13:46,714
And Zheng Decheng?

243
00:13:48,753 --> 00:13:51,033
Did his money ever pass through here?

244
00:13:51,553 --> 00:13:52,153
No.

245
00:13:52,834 --> 00:13:54,354
Mr. Zheng never did before.

246
00:13:55,834 --> 00:13:56,334
Really.

247
00:13:58,194 --> 00:14:01,633
The industrial park
was spearheaded by you, right?

248
00:14:02,393 --> 00:14:02,893
Yes.

249
00:14:03,673 --> 00:14:06,594
The town government even built a road
for your industrial park

250
00:14:06,873 --> 00:14:09,513
and took out an eight million yuan
bank loan for it, right?

251
00:14:10,793 --> 00:14:11,293
Right.

252
00:14:11,714 --> 00:14:14,234
It was one of the conditions
we negotiated with the town.

253
00:14:19,114 --> 00:14:20,114
Mr. Zheng

254
00:14:20,633 --> 00:14:23,393
agreed to so many conditions
for your industrial park

255
00:14:23,994 --> 00:14:26,673
and even personally took out the loan
to build the road for it.

256
00:14:27,153 --> 00:14:28,474
You two seem close.

257
00:14:31,273 --> 00:14:33,994
Sir, we do have a good relationship.

258
00:14:34,714 --> 00:14:36,513
But that's because
the town government leaders

259
00:14:36,594 --> 00:14:38,194
always think of the people.

260
00:14:38,553 --> 00:14:40,633
They handle matters fairly and strictly,

261
00:14:40,873 --> 00:14:41,553
never biased.

262
00:14:42,434 --> 00:14:45,393
Let's take the industrial park project
for example.

263
00:14:45,913 --> 00:14:47,834
We actually argued
during the negotiations.

264
00:14:48,994 --> 00:14:49,954
We slammed tables.

265
00:14:50,474 --> 00:14:52,074
Sorry, I'm just trying to make a point.

266
00:14:52,673 --> 00:14:53,194
It's fine.

267
00:14:54,114 --> 00:14:56,913
Then, in your daily work with Mr. Zheng,

268
00:14:57,594 --> 00:14:59,153
have you noticed any problems with him?

269
00:14:59,513 --> 00:15:00,234
(Factory Director's Office)
No problems.

270
00:15:01,074 --> 00:15:02,354
He's just too meticulous

271
00:15:02,913 --> 00:15:03,793
and too responsible

272
00:15:04,513 --> 00:15:05,873
and cares too much for the people.

273
00:15:16,314 --> 00:15:17,873
Alright, Ms. Gao, that's all for today.

274
00:15:19,114 --> 00:15:20,714
