379
00:19:59,033 --> 00:20:00,634
Alright, alright.

380
00:20:01,553 --> 00:20:04,874
Xuemei has had it really tough.
Let's cut our losses in time.

381
00:20:05,634 --> 00:20:07,714
Right, cut losses in time.

382
00:20:08,474 --> 00:20:10,434
I understand your concerns.

383
00:20:10,674 --> 00:20:12,553
So before I came here,

384
00:20:13,113 --> 00:20:15,273
I met with the leaders in Nanzhou.

385
00:20:15,634 --> 00:20:16,474
They said

386
00:20:17,033 --> 00:20:19,593
