for the first three years.

391
00:20:34,513 --> 00:20:36,073
Three years of factory rent.

392
00:20:36,194 --> 00:20:37,833
- Three years?
- The first three years.

393
00:20:37,833 --> 00:20:38,954
That's a huge perk.

394
00:20:39,154 --> 00:20:40,234
