412
00:21:20,033 --> 00:21:21,634
The specific preferential policies

413
00:21:22,073 --> 00:21:23,634
are all detailed in this contract.

414
00:21:24,154 --> 00:21:25,234
Everyone, take one.

415
00:21:25,874 --> 00:21:26,374
Here.

