443
00:22:26,914 --> 00:22:27,714
Keep it down.

444
00:22:28,033 --> 00:22:28,874
Okay, got it.

445
00:22:29,154 --> 00:22:30,634
Aren't we all worried

446
00:22:31,033 --> 00:22:33,954
about how this will affect Mr. Zheng?

447
00:22:34,394 --> 00:22:35,234
