448
00:22:35,634 --> 00:22:37,994
We're all wise people
who recognize reality.

449
00:22:38,113 --> 00:22:39,194
In three years,

450
00:22:39,513 --> 00:22:42,833
whether we're chubby wise people
or skinny wise people,

451
00:22:43,154 --> 00:22:44,394
when we've made it big,

452
00:22:45,194 --> 00:22:47,053
we can come back and repay Mr. Zheng.

453
00:22:47,434 --> 00:22:48,113
