454
00:22:48,273 --> 00:22:48,773
Right?

455
00:22:49,073 --> 00:22:50,033
It actually makes sense.

456
00:22:52,154 --> 00:22:53,513
Mr. Zheng has been so good to us.

457
00:22:53,513 --> 00:22:55,234
Wouldn't this seem...

458
00:22:55,553 --> 00:22:56,394
Oh, you old fossil.

459
00:22:56,600 --> 00:22:57,874
We'll never accept ourselves.

460
00:22:57,874 --> 00:22:59,073
Enough already.

461
00:22:59,914 --> 00:23:01,674
Hearing this about Mr. Zheng

462
00:23:02,434 --> 00:23:03,553
also hurts Xuemei.

463
00:23:03,994 --> 00:23:05,474
It hurts me more than any of you.

464
00:23:05,954 --> 00:23:07,874
What do we do now? It's about survival.

465
00:23:08,674 --> 00:23:10,593
