491
00:24:51,194 --> 00:24:51,694
Good.

492
00:24:51,954 --> 00:24:53,113
Then I need your cooperation.

493
00:24:53,434 --> 00:24:54,954
I must report to Ms. Li.

494
00:24:55,593 --> 00:24:56,273
May I?

495
00:24:56,274 --> 00:24:56,888
(Entry Agreement of Nanzhou
Changjia Printing Industrial Park)

496
00:25:02,674 --> 00:25:03,313
Ms. Li,

497
00:25:04,234 --> 00:25:05,033
emotionally,

498
00:25:05,833 --> 00:25:07,234
leaving feels wrong.

499
00:25:08,634 --> 00:25:09,513
You and Mr. Zheng,

500
00:25:10,753 --> 00:25:12,194
along with cadres like him,

501
00:25:12,914 --> 00:25:13,833
are great leaders.

502
00:25:14,154 --> 00:25:15,474
You've supported us tremendously.

503
00:25:15,994 --> 00:25:17,833
We're not ungrateful people.

504
00:25:18,033 --> 00:25:19,273
- Exactly.
- Right.

505
00:25:19,513 --> 00:25:20,833
But business

506
00:25:21,553 --> 00:25:23,073
isn't just about sentiment.

507
00:25:23,674 --> 00:25:26,994
