508
00:25:28,113 --> 00:25:30,234
So we must keep an escape route open.

509
00:25:31,194 --> 00:25:32,474
Please try to understand.

510
00:25:32,753 --> 00:25:33,513
I don't understand.

511
00:25:37,714 --> 00:25:39,033
I don't get the escape route.

512
00:25:39,874 --> 00:25:41,714
Have we ever given ourselves
an escape route?

513
00:25:42,674 --> 00:25:44,634
