523
00:26:12,994 --> 00:26:15,608
Yet she risked her health
to come see you all

524
00:26:15,608 --> 00:26:16,954
to ease your mind.

525
00:26:17,688 --> 00:26:18,744
That's a genuine feeling.

526
00:26:19,874 --> 00:26:21,593
Ms. Li believes you, Gao Xuemei,

527
00:26:22,073 --> 00:26:23,914
