528
00:26:24,513 --> 00:26:25,353
She trusts you.

529
00:26:26,073 --> 00:26:27,353
Yet you urged abandoning ship.

530
00:26:27,874 --> 00:26:28,753
I don't understand.

531
00:26:29,914 --> 00:26:30,553
Guys,

532
00:26:31,113 --> 00:26:32,994
