for so long,

547
00:27:17,154 --> 00:27:19,113
I know him, and I trust him.

548
00:27:19,634 --> 00:27:21,434
I swear on my Party loyalty

549
00:27:22,154 --> 00:27:23,714
that he has absolutely never done

550
00:27:23,874 --> 00:27:26,434
any of the things mentioned
in that news story.

551
00:27:28,634 --> 00:27:31,313
You've known him
even longer than I have.

552
00:27:31,753 --> 00:27:32,833
I believe you know better

553
00:27:33,553 --> 00:27:35,434
what kind of man he is than I do.

554
00:27:36,273 --> 00:27:38,113
And I believe

555
00:27:38,954 --> 00:27:41,954
the Party will investigate thoroughly
and clear his name.

556
00:27:43,954 --> 00:27:46,994
Times have provided chances
to both Yuehai and you.

557
00:27:49,033 --> 00:27:50,833
You arrived in Yuehai,

558
00:27:51,394 --> 00:27:52,994
and then your business started to grow.

559
00:27:53,714 --> 00:27:55,874
Now you are the masters of this city.

560
00:27:56,674 --> 00:27:58,634
Yuehai is a place to come and go freely.

561
00:27:59,033 --> 00:28:00,154
If you wish to leave,

562
00:28:00,593 --> 00:28:02,634
I have no right to keep you here.

563
00:28:03,634 --> 00:28:04,353
But,

564
00:28:05,154 --> 00:28:07,513
since Yuehai once gave you
the chance to earn money,

565
00:28:08,793 --> 00:28:10,194
I now beg you

566
00:28:11,313 --> 00:28:14,434
to give Yuehai a chance.

567
00:28:20,474 --> 00:28:21,513
- Ms. Li!
- Ms. Li!

568
00:28:21,593 --> 00:28:22,093
- Please don't!
- Please!

569
00:28:22,273 --> 00:28:22,994
Please don't.

570
00:28:23,113 --> 00:28:23,714
Ms. Li,

571
00:28:23,874 --> 00:28:25,234
please don't do this.

572
00:28:32,234 --> 00:28:33,553
Wait. Ms. Li.

573
00:28:36,513 --> 00:28:37,033
Please.

574
00:28:37,234 --> 00:28:38,313
Please don't.

575
00:28:41,634 --> 00:28:43,674
No affection. It's better to leave.

576
00:28:44,434 --> 00:28:45,113
Stay.

577
00:28:45,434 --> 00:28:47,194
Stay for a meal.

578
00:29:45,353 --> 00:29:47,154
Don't think
I'm just swaying with the wind.

579
00:29:49,513 --> 00:29:50,313
In business,

580
00:29:51,833 --> 00:29:54,474
it's all hard-earned money.
We have to consider everything.

581
00:29:56,313 --> 00:29:59,033
At first, I just wanted
to minimize everyone's losses quickly.

582
00:29:59,833 --> 00:30:01,474
Because I knew
we couldn't afford to lose.

583
00:30:03,194 --> 00:30:04,634
But right now, I realize

584
00:30:05,753 --> 00:30:06,553
we were wrong.

585
00:30:07,593 --> 00:30:08,793
At least I was wrong.

586
00:30:14,113 --> 00:30:15,234
Thinking about it carefully,

587
00:30:16,553 --> 00:30:18,914
there's no such thing
as a completely safe venture.

588
00:30:19,353 --> 00:30:20,033
Right?

589
00:30:25,353 --> 00:30:26,113
This time,

590
00:30:28,113 --> 00:30:29,874
I'm willing to bet on Yuehai.

591
00:30:33,394 --> 00:30:35,714
Well? Time to show where you stand.

592
00:30:37,714 --> 00:30:38,313
Alright.

593
00:30:38,674 --> 00:30:40,073
Since Xuemei put it that way,

594
00:30:40,593 --> 00:30:41,674
we should follow her lead.

595
00:30:41,914 --> 00:30:42,414
No.

596
00:30:43,073 --> 00:30:44,313
- Don't follow me.
- Right.

597
00:30:44,994 --> 00:30:46,394
You should decide for yourselves.

598
00:30:47,154 --> 00:30:50,194
I never had much schooling.
Just a farm woman before.

599
00:30:51,434 --> 00:30:53,994
My success
isn't due to any special talent.

600
00:30:54,994 --> 00:30:56,753
I just happened to catch the right wave.

601
00:30:59,634 --> 00:31:01,073
Ms. Li was right earlier.

602
00:31:02,674 --> 00:31:04,273
We're the masters of this city.

603
00:31:05,394 --> 00:31:07,833
We built Yuehai from nothing together.

604
00:31:08,714 --> 00:31:09,994
Now it's facing tough times.

605
00:31:11,753 --> 00:31:12,714
We can't abandon it.

606
00:31:15,513 --> 00:31:16,833
I won't sign that contract.

607
00:31:17,474 --> 00:31:18,674
Anyone planning to sign?

608
00:31:19,474 --> 00:31:21,714
I already said I'm with you.

609
00:31:22,474 --> 00:31:24,113
We're the masters here, right?

610
00:31:24,793 --> 00:31:26,154
Good thing I didn't sign earlier.

611
00:31:31,194 --> 00:31:31,874
Okay.

612
00:31:32,714 --> 00:31:34,833
The contract I just signed
is invalid too.

613
00:31:35,874 --> 00:31:38,434
The one I signed is also invalid.

614
00:31:39,273 --> 00:31:40,434
We aren't signing, either.

615
00:31:41,753 --> 00:31:42,513
I'm not signing.

616
00:31:42,914 --> 00:31:43,753
I won't sign, either.

617
00:31:44,073 --> 00:31:44,833
I'm not signing.

618
00:31:45,353 --> 00:31:46,353
I never planned to sign.

619
00:31:48,113 --> 00:31:49,113
None of us will sign.

620
00:31:49,914 --> 00:31:50,414
Right.

621
00:31:50,674 --> 00:31:51,434
No one's signing.

622
00:32:08,793 --> 00:32:09,634
Thank you all.

623
00:32:21,714 --> 00:32:23,793
I swear on my character
that Mr. Zheng is clean.

624
00:32:24,394 --> 00:32:26,313
We've worked together since long ago.

625
00:32:27,714 --> 00:32:30,793
By the logic,
Mr. Zheng must have issues.

626
00:32:32,634 --> 00:32:33,134
Yes.

627
00:32:34,073 --> 00:32:34,914
There's one thing.

628
00:32:37,553 --> 00:32:38,234
Which one?

629
00:32:38,994 --> 00:32:39,714
People...

630
00:32:41,874 --> 00:32:44,414
To err is human, right?

631
00:32:45,194 --> 00:32:45,914
Elaborate.

632
00:32:49,353 --> 00:32:50,273
Who's badmouthing me?

633
00:32:52,513 --> 00:32:55,313
He raised turtles,
leading everyone into getting scammed.

634
00:32:55,553 --> 00:32:57,714
- He forced me to eat.
- Ten thousand yuan.

635
00:32:58,113 --> 00:32:59,613
He took on that loss alone

636
00:32:59,753 --> 00:33:00,914
and is still paying it off.

637
00:33:01,154 --> 00:33:02,793
Mr. Zheng's problem is...

638
00:33:03,113 --> 00:33:04,874
Said I had to gain five kilograms.

639
00:33:05,234 --> 00:33:07,194
I loaned him 2,000.
You say he has money?

640
00:33:07,474 --> 00:33:09,313
But he refuses to pay me.
Investigate him.

641
00:33:09,313 --> 00:33:10,513
And have him repay me quickly.

642
00:33:10,674 --> 00:33:13,234
He colluded with Ms. Li
to rig the scales.

643
00:33:13,593 --> 00:33:14,914
Later, he even locked me up.

644
00:33:15,194 --> 00:33:16,408
After I finished the accounts,

645
00:33:16,753 --> 00:33:19,154
he'd double-check them every week.

646
00:33:19,313 --> 00:33:21,353
I'm an extremely meticulous person.

647
00:33:21,553 --> 00:33:22,154
Right.

648
00:33:22,634 --> 00:33:24,593
Later, he ran to the site
to be the foreman.

649
00:33:24,753 --> 00:33:25,914
He did all my job.

650
00:33:26,474 --> 00:33:28,593
He works diligently

651
00:33:28,793 --> 00:33:29,954
and is self-sacrificing.

652
00:33:30,273 --> 00:33:31,513
He'd never seek personal gain.

653
00:33:31,634 --> 00:33:33,414
All other people have gotten rich.

654
00:33:33,513 --> 00:33:35,113
But look at him. Does he change clothes?

655
00:33:37,234 --> 00:33:38,313
Of course he does.

656
00:33:38,954 --> 00:33:40,920
But he wears the same clothes
for over a decade.

657
00:33:42,833 --> 00:33:43,553
What a secretary!

658
00:33:44,234 --> 00:33:45,313
You find no one like him.

659
00:33:45,434 --> 00:33:48,033
Am I foolish to work with him?
He's a true proletarian soldier.

660
00:33:48,434 --> 00:33:50,634
Even after my repeated checks,
he would run his own.

661
00:33:50,634 --> 00:33:52,593
And it wasn't enough.
He'd drag Ms. Li in

662
00:33:52,914 --> 00:33:54,154
for a third check.

663
00:33:55,033 --> 00:33:57,994
Mr. Xie, why are you so worked up?

664
00:33:58,353 --> 00:33:59,553
We haven't asked anything yet.

665
00:34:00,033 --> 00:34:02,234
Am I worked up? I'm just stating facts.

666
00:34:03,833 --> 00:34:05,194
Do you know what we'll ask?

667
00:34:05,674 --> 00:34:06,174
No.

668
00:34:06,394 --> 00:34:07,194
This has gone cold.

669
00:34:08,274 --> 00:34:10,673
Would you mind taking off your T-shirt?

670
00:34:14,354 --> 00:34:15,113
Take...

671
00:34:16,474 --> 00:34:17,673
Take it off?

672
00:34:24,754 --> 00:34:25,553
We are aware

673
00:34:25,954 --> 00:34:28,914
that highway bandit Zheng Zhiqiang
stabbed you.

674
00:34:29,113 --> 00:34:30,593
We'd like to see the wound.

675
00:34:30,994 --> 00:34:31,994
No need to take it off.

676
00:34:32,153 --> 00:34:32,653
Right?

677
00:34:32,994 --> 00:34:34,153
There is a female here.

678
00:34:34,354 --> 00:34:35,113
Sorry.

679
00:34:35,914 --> 00:34:38,354
Gao Xuemei is your wife, right?

680
00:34:40,073 --> 00:34:40,713
That's right.

681
00:34:42,414 --> 00:34:42,914
Why?

682
00:34:42,914 --> 00:34:45,274
Are you involved in
Chunmei Printery's daily operations?

683
00:34:47,153 --> 00:34:47,874
Am I involved?

684
00:34:48,193 --> 00:34:48,994
Here's the thing.

685
00:34:49,153 --> 00:34:51,173
What's there to hide about this, right?

686
00:34:51,274 --> 00:34:52,354
I was indeed injured.

687
00:34:56,113 --> 00:34:56,874
From what we know,

688
00:34:57,394 --> 00:34:58,794
during your tenure as Yuehai's

689
00:34:59,754 --> 00:35:00,834
deputy mayor,

690
00:35:01,193 --> 00:35:02,153
Chunmei Printery

691
00:35:02,354 --> 00:35:04,354
underwent a meteoric rise,
from a tiny factory

692
00:35:04,794 --> 00:35:07,233
worth tens of thousands annually
to Yuehai's

693
00:35:07,914 --> 00:35:09,193
million-yuan flagship.

694
00:35:09,593 --> 00:35:10,754
Is this correct?

695
00:35:12,274 --> 00:35:12,794
Yes.

696
00:35:14,233 --> 00:35:16,274
That's all Xuemei's doing.

697
00:35:16,754 --> 00:35:19,193
She built its success single-handedly.

698
00:35:19,553 --> 00:35:21,314
It has nothing to do with Mr. Zheng.

699
00:35:21,593 --> 00:35:23,640
What's Zheng Zhiqiang's relation
to Zheng Decheng?

700
00:35:23,713 --> 00:35:24,434
They're relatives.

701
00:35:25,073 --> 00:35:27,994
Mr. Zheng has an older brother.
Just the two of them.

702
00:35:28,434 --> 00:35:30,354
His older brother is Zheng Desheng.

703
00:35:30,874 --> 00:35:32,553
Zheng Desheng has three sons.

704
00:35:33,193 --> 00:35:34,834
The eldest, the second,
and the youngest.

705
00:35:35,073 --> 00:35:36,874
The third son is Zheng Zhiqiang.

706
00:35:37,073 --> 00:35:38,994
Don't explain. Just answer.

707
00:35:39,954 --> 00:35:40,834
As we understand it,

708
00:35:41,153 --> 00:35:43,994
the industrial park
was initiated by your wife.

709
00:35:44,434 --> 00:35:46,434
The town government even took out

710
00:35:46,794 --> 00:35:48,952
an eight-million bank loan
for its road construction.

711
00:35:49,193 --> 00:35:50,354
Is this correct?

712
00:35:51,474 --> 00:35:53,874
Absolutely impossible.
How could he shield anyone?

713
00:35:54,434 --> 00:35:55,633
You know what? Mr. Zheng

714
00:35:55,633 --> 00:35:58,073
despises it when relatives
or friends pull this stuff.

715
00:35:58,593 --> 00:35:59,673
He has a fierce temper.

716
00:35:59,713 --> 00:36:02,354
A road less than two kilometers long

717
00:36:02,633 --> 00:36:04,113
needed an eight-million loan?

718
00:36:04,394 --> 00:36:05,553
Is it an ordinary road?

719
00:36:06,914 --> 00:36:08,434
There was a mountain there originally.

720
00:36:08,633 --> 00:36:11,073
It looks flat now
because we blew up that mountain.

721
00:36:12,033 --> 00:36:12,914
How much do you think

722
00:36:13,394 --> 00:36:14,113
that would cost?

723
00:36:14,354 --> 00:36:16,954
We only spent just over four million
blowing it up.

724
00:36:17,153 --> 00:36:17,754
That's correct.

725
00:36:18,434 --> 00:36:19,394
After blowing it up,

726
00:36:19,673 --> 00:36:22,434
we had 3,926,300 yuan left.

727
00:36:22,794 --> 00:36:24,113
My biggest concern is

728
00:36:24,874 --> 00:36:26,994
Mr. Zheng himself
knowingly breaking the law.

729
00:36:27,954 --> 00:36:29,354
He can't stand such a thing.

730
00:36:29,354 --> 00:36:32,233
If he finds out immediately,
he might resort to violence.

731
00:36:32,633 --> 00:36:34,553
When we were short on funds,
no one asked.

732
00:36:34,914 --> 00:36:36,033
Why ask now?

733
00:36:36,354 --> 00:36:37,434
It wasn't enough.

734
00:36:38,233 --> 00:36:39,384
Then I came up with an idea.

735
00:36:39,994 --> 00:36:42,593
We used the blasted rocks
to pave the road right there.

736
00:36:43,073 --> 00:36:46,073
That saved on material costs

737
00:36:46,633 --> 00:36:49,794
and reduced the expense

738
00:36:50,033 --> 00:36:51,794
of transporting and disposing
of the rubble.

739
00:36:57,354 --> 00:36:58,033
Sir,

740
00:36:58,673 --> 00:37:01,474
how much longer
will this investigation take?

741
00:37:02,073 --> 00:37:03,434
Where is Mr. Zheng now?

742
00:37:03,794 --> 00:37:07,794
When will Yuehai's accounts be unfrozen?

743
00:37:08,754 --> 00:37:09,474
Why?

744
00:37:10,553 --> 00:37:12,394
The road construction sites are stopped.

745
00:37:12,754 --> 00:37:15,033
But you know what?
This is critical right now.

746
00:37:15,153 --> 00:37:17,513
We are at the most crucial stage
of construction.

747
00:37:17,593 --> 00:37:18,834
With all the accounts frozen,

748
00:37:18,834 --> 00:37:19,513
all our sites...

749
00:37:19,513 --> 00:37:20,394
Mr. Tan. Mr. Tan.

750
00:37:20,593 --> 00:37:22,033
We understand the situation.

751
00:37:22,033 --> 00:37:23,593
You may leave now.

752
00:37:23,754 --> 00:37:26,553
We will notify you
when we require further assistance.

753
00:37:27,193 --> 00:37:27,914
Sorry.

754
00:37:28,394 --> 00:37:30,754
But sir, please try to expedite this.

755
00:37:30,774 --> 00:37:31,274
Okay.

756
00:37:31,274 --> 00:37:31,914
Take care.

757
00:38:08,994 --> 00:38:10,073
This is Mr. Zheng.

758
00:38:20,874 --> 00:38:21,553
You...

759
00:38:22,394 --> 00:38:23,113
are Zheng Shuji?

760
00:38:23,354 --> 00:38:23,854
Yes.

761
00:38:24,033 --> 00:38:25,354
My name is Zheng Shuji.
[*Shuji sounds like Secretary in Chinese]

762
00:38:27,354 --> 00:38:28,553
Come on. Sit.

763
00:38:31,874 --> 00:38:34,153
Your full name is
actually 'Zheng Shuji'?

764
00:38:34,354 --> 00:38:36,474
Correct, my name is Zheng Shuji.

765
00:38:40,713 --> 00:38:41,713
(Household Register)
This is my household register.

766
00:38:42,424 --> 00:38:44,113
(Zheng Shuji)

767
00:38:44,113 --> 00:38:46,193
Here are the land use certificates.
Take a look.

768
00:38:51,570 --> 00:38:55,160
(Land Use Certificate)
(Zheng Shuji)

769
00:39:00,834 --> 00:39:01,474
It's fine.

770
00:39:01,994 --> 00:39:02,994
Alright,

771
00:39:03,914 --> 00:39:05,374
you may go. Take your things.

772
00:39:05,474 --> 00:39:07,113
Thank you for cooperating.

773
00:39:07,673 --> 00:39:08,434
You may go now.

774
00:39:08,874 --> 00:39:09,673
Escort him out.

775
00:39:09,794 --> 00:39:10,314
Okay.

776
00:39:10,593 --> 00:39:11,274
Follow me.

777
00:39:11,394 --> 00:39:12,113
Alright.

778
00:39:13,113 --> 00:39:13,754
Take care.

779
00:39:19,354 --> 00:39:21,994
How could someone
actually be named 'Zheng Shuji'?

780
00:39:22,153 --> 00:39:22,914
Exactly.

781
00:39:23,673 --> 00:39:25,513
Sir, I think we should question

782
00:39:25,553 --> 00:39:26,834
those deputy mayors some more.

783
00:39:27,314 --> 00:39:28,954
Feels like
they're all putting on an act.

784
00:39:29,394 --> 00:39:30,914
Maybe there's more they're hiding.

785
00:39:31,394 --> 00:39:33,314
Yes, they are definitely acting.

786
00:39:33,874 --> 00:39:35,713
After all, they're doing it
for Zheng Decheng.

787
00:39:37,073 --> 00:39:38,193
But what they said is true.

788
00:39:39,274 --> 00:39:41,673
That industrial park
and the eight million...

789
00:39:43,474 --> 00:39:44,553
These cadres

790
00:39:46,274 --> 00:39:47,033
are something.

791
00:39:49,553 --> 00:39:50,193
But it's okay.

792
00:39:50,513 --> 00:39:52,553
When we investigate,
we have to trust the evidence.

793
00:39:53,073 --> 00:39:54,593
New evidence will surely surface.

794
00:39:56,073 --> 00:39:58,513
How's the investigation on your end?

795
00:39:59,593 --> 00:40:01,354
Besides the property thing of Mr. Zheng,

796
00:40:01,794 --> 00:40:03,834
we've cross-checked
Yuehai's accounts at least

797
00:40:04,673 --> 00:40:05,434
three times.

798
00:40:06,553 --> 00:40:07,434
We found no issues.

799
00:40:08,754 --> 00:40:09,673
Mr. Zheng...

800
00:40:11,113 --> 00:40:11,834
What about you?

801
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:13,713
The visits
to the self-employed individuals?

802
00:40:13,994 --> 00:40:16,714
We visited 187 self-employed businesses
along Binhai Road.

803
00:40:16,714 --> 00:40:18,593
No useful leads have been found for now.

804
00:40:20,994 --> 00:40:21,633
It's normal.

805
00:40:22,954 --> 00:40:23,794
If they

806
00:40:24,033 --> 00:40:26,633
had any under-the-table money dealings
with Zheng Decheng,

807
00:40:26,954 --> 00:40:28,153
them keeping quiet is normal.

808
00:40:31,754 --> 00:40:32,794
Alright, let's think

809
00:40:33,754 --> 00:40:34,713
from a different angle.

810
00:40:35,274 --> 00:40:35,994
A new approach.

811
00:40:36,754 --> 00:40:40,033
Go interview
some ordinary workers in Yuehai.

812
00:40:40,954 --> 00:40:41,513
Okay.

813
00:40:41,633 --> 00:40:42,193
- Okay.
- Okay.

814
00:40:42,874 --> 00:40:43,713
I almost forgot.

815
00:40:43,914 --> 00:40:44,513
Mr. Liu,

816
00:40:46,713 --> 00:40:48,193
here's the receipt for a TV set.

817
00:40:48,394 --> 00:40:49,553
(Payment Receipt)
Found by Qian Changyuan.

818
00:40:52,513 --> 00:40:53,113
See?

819
00:40:54,394 --> 00:40:56,713
